WEBVTT

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:11.343
Amen. He said there's going to be a new wave of patriotism coming out, and that's whenever I saw Trump and a red wave coming out of Michigan.

00:00:11.344 --> 00:00:18.353
Then I saw Oklahoma, and there were embers of people, and they all had torches throughout Oklahoma.

00:00:18.354 --> 00:00:26.166
They were raising up these torches that looked like fire, and they were bringing forth a new patriotism upon the nation.

00:00:26.168 --> 00:00:30.810
It was being birthed and it just kept spreading like fire all throughout America.

00:00:30.811 --> 00:00:45.194
I saw Trump rising up, and then I saw an attempt on his life: this bullet flew by his ear and it came so close to his head that it busted his eardrum.

00:00:45.195 --> 00:00:49.934
He fell to his knees during this timeframe and he started worshiping the Lord.

00:00:49.934 --> 00:01:01.259
He got radically born again during this timeframe—I'm talking, people say he's saved now, but he becomes really on fire for Jesus from what I saw coming.

00:01:01.260 --> 00:01:07.625
Then I saw people interceding, and I saw him winning the presidency.

00:01:07.626 --> 00:01:24.894
The Lord showed me it would go clear into the summer; great persecution would come on him through the judges and through the law and all these people trying to sue him, but there would be a stop to it and things would start to break free toward the fall.

00:01:24.895 --> 00:01:31.358
Then I saw him winning the election through the patriots coming out and voting.

00:01:31.359 --> 00:01:40.352
Then there will be a great economic crash. I saw they had a great economic plan, a crash worse than the Great Depression.

00:01:40.353 --> 00:01:49.716
The Lord warned me about this; it would be a great dark time, but I saw paddles coming upon America's soil like a shocking of the soil.

00:01:49.718 --> 00:01:57.600
I saw Donald Trump praying in the Oval Office and he was weeping before the Lord with his hands on his head.

00:01:57.601 --> 00:02:16.948
There were ministers and people—I don't know if they were senators or congresspeople—I just saw them pacing back and forth inside of the White House, the Oval Office, and they were interceding all inside there.

00:02:16.949 --> 00:02:37.535
I could feel the presence of the Lord so strong on this. Then I could see that darkness, the heaviness upon America with the financial crisis I saw coming, started to lift above the trees and I saw the blue and the green times—good times—coming back again.

00:02:37.536 --> 00:02:45.726
But the Lord said it would be a season of a shaking, and it would be a shaking.

00:02:45.727 --> 00:02:53.674
In this, basically, he was not done with America; there would be a great revival.

00:02:53.675 --> 00:02:56.708
It's not all doom and gloom; that's what he said. 'The sky is not falling.

00:02:56.709 --> 00:03:02.424
It's just a time—people would say this is judgment,'and the Lord said, 'Do not call this judgment.

00:03:02.425 --> 00:03:10.360
It's not my judgment; it's a correction. There's a correction coming.

